\{chapter single_07}

	\{section -name L07MQ01}
The Pirates have followed you across the sea and will continue to hunt you on dry land. At the moment, the enemy is much stronger than you are. Escape to the desert until you find a way to improve your chances of winning.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Escape the Pirates and flee to the desert!
\{p}
2) Your Heroes need to survive.
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) Follow the dried-out river bed!
\{p}
2) Don’t try to fight the Pirates – it would be futile!
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07MQ02}
Find a way into the Dustriders’ city! Once you’ve arrived, Taslow will sabotage the Water Temple, thus fulfilling the prophecy.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Take Cole, Stina, Béla, and Taslow all the way to the Water Temple!
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) More than one path leads to the destination!
\{p}
2) Some of Taslow’s workers are taking care of food resources in the North. They will help you build your army.
\{p}
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07MQ03}
Hold your position against the SEAS! If the Black Widows reach Taslow’s abode, you have failed your mission.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Destroy all Black Widows!
\{p}
2) Prevent the SEAS from reaching Taslow’s house!
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) Taslow Towers are very effective against mechanical units.
\{p}
2) The SEAS land in various places and at different times. Use this fact to your advantage.
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07SQ01}
A herd of Gallimimus threatens Taslow’s farmers and prevents them from doing their work. Destroy the nest and kill them! As Taslow is your ally, you can now also control his farmers.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Find and destroy all Gallimimus and their nest!
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) The herd of Gallimimus can be spread across a large area. If you find and attack their nest first, they will come back and attack you in turn!
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07SQ02}
You are under attack from a Dustriders military camp. If you want to get to the city on land, you will have to cross this camp. The Dustriders’ attacks will only cease once the military camp is destroyed.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Destroy the Military Camp of the hostile Dustriders!
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) There are various paths you can use to attack the camp.
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07SQ03}
From here, you can reach the Dustrider city gate without interference. Initially, the Dustrider city is neutral towards you. The towers will only begin to fire if you attack the town. With a bit of luck, you might be able to defeat the city guards. But beware: If the military camp is alerted, the troops stationed there will immediately attack you.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Approach the guards at the city wall in a peaceful manner to avoid coming under fire from the towers.
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) You can stage a surprise attack from the rear – but be careful, the city will then not be neutral any longer and it will be more difficult to get to the city gate.
\{p}
2) You have got here in a peaceful manner. If you stay peaceful, you can face the city guards without a fight which saves you strength and time.
\{p}
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07SQ04}
Along this path are the Dustriders’ production and residential buildings where they produce their supplies.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Move to the other side of the city and destroy the production and residential buildings of the Dustriders.
\{p}
2) Then enter the Water Temple!
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) If you take the long way, nobody will be able to put paid to your plans once you’ve destroyed the Water Temple. This will protect you from nasty surprises!
\{p}
	\{/section}

	\{section -name L07SQ05}
If you construct Taslow Towers close to the buildings, defeating the SEAS Black Widows will be much easier!\{p}
\{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Build Taslow Towers at the three predefined positions (marked with a "?").
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) Taslow needs to be on Level 4 in order to construct Taslow Towers.
\{p}
2) You need to hurry up, the SEAS are approaching fast!
	\{/section}

		\{section -name L07SQ06}
There are secret locations in the sea where you can find two treasures.
\{p} \{p}
Objectives:
\{p}
1) Find two Treasures.
\{p} \{p}
Hints:
\{p}
1) One of the artifacts is hidden on the main land, but you can only reach the spot via the sea.
\{p}
	\{/section}
\{/chapter}


